article_title: Iowa's Grassley will seek a sixth Senate term in 2016

article_metadata.description: Iowa's long-time liberal Dem Sen. Tom Harkin decided to make an early announcement that he wouldn't seek another term in 2014, creating a fairly wide open race for the seat he has occupied since 1985.

og.description: If Charles Grassley wins, he'll be 89 when his next erm ends.
og.title: Iowa's Grassley will seek a sixth Senate term in 2016
